It's about 5 lines without all the brackets, but the idea is put all the greater elements first, and then put all the lesser elements. Pair max with median - 1, max - 1 with median - 2, etc.

The inspiration behind this idea is that we can't pair max with min because at the end of it, median and gonna be paired with median and they may be equal! So in order to address that, let's pair max with median.
