# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1) copy the nums array
2) sort the sort array
3) itarate nums from index 1 to length and increment by 2 add sorted array of last index and decrement index;
4) same for nums from index 0 to length and increment by 2.

